window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Bobby N. Kowen is living his life to the fullest. He’s making friends, he’s learning new things all the time, he’s falling in love, he’s having adventures. He’s doing more in a single week than most of us experience in a lifetime.</p> <p>But that’s the thing. That one week is all that Bobby has. Birth to death...in just seven days.</p> <p>Bobby’s life is truly a race against time. No one who meets him will ever be the same. And they will each wonder: Do we live too long to really appreciate how precious life is?</p>"; 
